---
title: "WINDWOODS"
---

- Wind blasted ground that was once a sea
- Tonnes of tumbleweeds
- Lots of hole pocked stones that cause whistling sounds. These holes were created piddocks (bivalves) when the area was underwater

- Currently safe from Amazonia as her drones cannot handle the wind.


Keep this pretty bare with descriptions and some random encoutner tables

Random encounters

- Gitant Ornagutan refugees from the [REDWOODS](/DENDROSPHAERA/REDWOODS.qmd)



- Contains a base for the Dendrosphaera resistance
  - Create some stats for normal resitance members
  - Create a leader and a few team leads
  - They try to fight Amazonia's forces and help refugees